'''Susie Porter''' (born [[January 8]], [[1971]]) is an [[Wikipedia:Australians|Australian]] actress who played [[Hermione Bagwa]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]. She also voiced [[FLO]], the other waitress of [[Dex's Diner]].<ref>{{DB|droid|wa7|FLO (WA-7)}}</ref>

